            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Worst school ever. They do not care about the facilities, ur child's future. They care only about one thing that is money. The fees is very high i.e. ₹1.20 laks p.a. Don't let ur child study here. Just a waste of time and money. Many cases of bullying, beating, fighting, ragging, wape, drugs but no action has been taken on. Also the teachers are not skilled. Transport is very high i.e. ₹4-5000 per month but no facilities. Most of the buses do not have a first aid kit.\nNot even a skilled doctor. No summer camp, no creative club. Overall, the worst school in the whole Noida.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
