          "datePublished": "2023-07-29",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Not at all a good school. They take ₹1.20 lakh p.a. but r not providing us with proper facilities. No proper canteen, no auditorium, no A/C buses, no smart way of studying. The smartboards r just a showpiece. Most of them don't work. Some work  but are outdated. Also the transport fee is so high i.e. ₹4-5000 per month. Coming by an auto rickshaw would be cheaper. Also many good teachers left the school. The new teachers are not at all skilled. Also, they say that there are many sports in school but in reality, there are very less equipments and the too are broken or damaged. The bats are damaged, stumps are broken, football doesn't have air. Also, they say that there are many clubs in the school (14 creative clubs) but in reality there are no clubs.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
