          "reviewBody": "One of the worst school.\nFor Nursery entrance  3 teacher seats and take interview of 4 year kid and finally they are not selected my Kid who is selected in DPS Noida after that.\nI don't understand the procedure they have for entrance, all are just a way of earning nothing else.",
