            "name": "Mohit Chauhan"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-09-09",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Putting mental pressure and still giving online material for the work and saying \" we will not share any material online to avoid screentime\" is a biggest irony. I don't know whether the school staff will read this review and take action on it but its just a status symbol for most of the parents nothing else.\nGiving many worksheets left no time with students to do the self study or self exploration. They say \"we believe in passion of children but we will not give them time to explore their passion\"\n.\n2 assignment sheets per day and not giving even a single day in between just rat race and syllabus complete.\n\nMost people preferred this school bcoz they think that it must be the good school nature bcoz all so called showoff people children study here but it totally opposite.\nThis school is famous for aggroancy in child. Children literally do 18+ talk which is the worst atmosphere.\n\nI request this school to reduce the homework load from kids and stop being a hypocrite.\n\nRegards\nEx-student.",
          "publisher": {
